text: The 2022–23 FC Liefering season was the 10th season of FC Liefering in the second league. Liefering finished 9th. Despite a contract until 2024, the club ended its collaboration with head coach Ingolitsch at the end of the season.Ligaportal.at (German) ==Squad == * Goalkeepers: 34 Jonas Krumrey, 32 Balazs Toth, ?
